Class DefaultChangeMasterService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultChangeMasterService

    ChangeMasterService

    @Named
public class DefaultChangeMasterService
extends Object
implements ChangeMasterService

    This API enables you to read change master data via an OData service.

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_CHANGEMASTER
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1705
    Communication Scenario:Product Lifecycle Management - Master Data Integration (SAP_COM_0105)
    Scope Items:Change Number Configuration (1O5)
